contents:
[package]
name = "cxx-kde-frameworks"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
build = "build/main.rs"
links = "cxx-kde-frameworks"

[dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.121"

[dependencies.cxx-qt]
git = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt"
branch = "main"

[dependencies.cxx-qt-lib]
git = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt"
branch = "main"
features = [ "qt_full",]

[dependencies.cxx-qt-lib-extras]
git = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt"
branch = "main"

[build-dependencies.cxx-qt-build]
git = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt"
branch = "main"
features = [ "link_qt_object_files",]

[package]
name = "cxx-qt"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Andrew Hayzen <andrew.hayzen@kdab.com>", "Gerhard de Clercq <gerhard.declercq@kdab.com>", "Leon Matthes <leon.matthes@kdab.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Safe interop between Rust and Qt"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
homepage = "https://kdab.github.io/cxx-qt/book/"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "cxx", "ffi", "QML", "Qt",]
categories = [ "api-bindings", "gui",]
rust-version = "1.77.2"
links = "cxx-qt"

[dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.95"
static_assertions = "1.1.0"
thiserror = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.95"

[dependencies.cxx-qt-macro]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-macro"
version = "0.7.0"

[build-dependencies.cxx-qt-build]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-build"
version = "0.7.0"

[build-dependencies.qt-build-utils]
path = "crates/qt-build-utils"
version = "0.7.0"

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[package]
name = "cxx-qt-build"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Andrew Hayzen <andrew.hayzen@kdab.com>", "Gerhard de Clercq <gerhard.declercq@kdab.com>", "Leon Matthes <leon.matthes@kdab.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Helpers for integrating `cxx-qt` crate into a Cargo build"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
rust-version = "1.77.2"

[dependencies]
cxx-gen = "0.7.121"
proc-macro2 = "1.0"
quote = "1.0"
codespan-reporting = "0.11"
version_check = "0.9"
serde_json = "1.0"

[features]
link_qt_object_files = [ "qt-build-utils/link_qt_object_files",]

[dependencies.cc]
version = "1.0.100"
features = [ "parallel",]

[dependencies.cxx-qt-gen]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-gen"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.qt-build-utils]
path = "crates/qt-build-utils"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "default", "derive",]

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[package]
name = "cxx-qt-gen"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Andrew Hayzen <andrew.hayzen@kdab.com>", "Gerhard de Clercq <gerhard.declercq@kdab.com>", "Leon Matthes <leon.matthes@kdab.com>", "Ben Ford <ben.ford@kdab.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Code generation for integrating `cxx-qt` into higher level tools"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
exclude = [ "update_expected.sh",]
rust-version = "1.64.0"

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0"
quote = "1.0"
convert_case = "0.6.0"
clang-format = "0.3"
indoc = "2.0"

[dev-dependencies]
pretty_assertions = "1.2"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0"
features = [ "extra-traits", "full",]

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[package]
name = "cxx-qt-lib"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Andrew Hayzen <andrew.hayzen@kdab.com>", "Gerhard de Clercq <gerhard.declercq@kdab.com>", "Leon Matthes <leon.matthes@kdab.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Qt types for integrating `cxx-qt` crate with `cxx`"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
exclude = [ "**/generate.sh",]
links = "cxx-qt-lib"
rust-version = "1.77.2"

[dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.95"

[features]
full = [ "qt_full", "serde", "url", "time", "rgb", "http", "chrono", "bytes",]
default = []
qt_full = [ "qt_gui", "qt_qml", "qt_quickcontrols",]
qt_gui = []
qt_qml = []
qt_quickcontrols = []
bytes = [ "dep:bytes",]
chrono = [ "dep:chrono",]
http = [ "dep:http",]
rgb = [ "dep:rgb",]
time = [ "dep:time",]
url = [ "dep:url",]
serde = [ "dep:serde",]
link_qt_object_files = [ "cxx-qt-build/link_qt_object_files",]

[dependencies.cxx-qt]
path = "crates/cxx-qt"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.bytes]
version = "1.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.27"
optional = true

[dependencies.http]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.rgb]
version = "0.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.time]
version = "0.3.20"
optional = true

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[build-dependencies.cxx-qt-build]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-build"
version = "0.7.0"

[build-dependencies.qt-build-utils]
path = "crates/qt-build-utils"
version = "0.7.0"

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[package]
name = "cxx-qt-lib-extras"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Laurent Montel <laurent.montel@kdab.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Extra Qt types for integrating `cxx-qt` crate with `cxx` that are not available in `cxx-qt-lib`"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
links = "cxx-qt-lib-extras"
rust-version = "1.77.2"

[dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.95"

[features]
default = []
link_qt_object_files = [ "cxx-qt-build/link_qt_object_files",]

[dependencies.cxx-qt]
path = "crates/cxx-qt"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.cxx-qt-lib]
features = [ "qt_full",]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-lib"
version = "0.7.0"

[build-dependencies.cxx-qt-build]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-build"
version = "0.7.0"

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[package]
name = "cxx-qt-macro"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Andrew Hayzen <andrew.hayzen@kdab.com>", "Leon Matthes <leon.matthes@kdab.com>", "Gerhard de Clercq <gerhard.declercq@kdab.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "A set of macros for Qt/C++ interop in Rust"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
homepage = "https://kdab.github.io/cxx-qt/book/"
rust-version = "1.77.2"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
cxx = "1.0.95"

[dependencies.cxx-qt-gen]
path = "crates/cxx-qt-gen"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0"
features = [ "extra-traits", "full",]

[dev-dependencies.cxx-qt]
path = "crates/cxx-qt"
version = "0.7.0"

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[[bench]]
name = "benchmark"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "retail_benchmark"
harness = false
required-features = [ "retail_game_testing",]

[package]
name = "physis"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = [ "Joshua Goins <josh@redstrate.com>",]
edition = "2021"
description = "Interact with XIV game data."
license = "GPL-3.0"
homepage = "https://xiv.zone/physis"
repository = "https://github.com/redstrate/Physis"
keywords = [ "ffxiv", "modding",]
documentation = "https://docs.xiv.zone/docs/physis/"
readme = "README.md"

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "7"

[dev-dependencies]
hmac-sha512 = "1"
crc = "3"

[features]
default = [ "visual_data",]
game_install = []
visual_data = [ "dep:half", "dep:bitflags", "dep:texture2ddecoder",]
retail_game_testing = []
patch_testing = [ "game_install",]

[dependencies]
modular-bitfield = "0.11"

[profile.release]
lto = true

[dev-dependencies.brunch]
version = "0.5.3"
default-features = false

[dependencies.binrw]
version = "0.14"
features = [ "std",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
features = [ "std",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.libz-sys]
version = "1.1"

[dependencies.half]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.bitflags]
version = "1.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.texture2ddecoder]
version = "0.1"
optional = true

[package.metadata.system-deps.libunshield]
version = "1.4"
feature = "game_install"

[package]
name = "qt-build-utils"
version = "0.7.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Be Wilson <be.wilson@kdab.com>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Build script helper for linking Qt libraries and using moc code generator. Intended to be used together with cc, cpp_build, or cxx_build"
repository = "https://github.com/KDAB/cxx-qt/"
rust-version = "1.77.2"

[dependencies]
versions = "6.3"
thiserror = "1.0"

[features]
link_qt_object_files = []

[dependencies.cc]
version = "1.0.100"
features = [ "parallel",]

[lints.clippy]
incompatible_msrv = "deny"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://invent.kde.org/libraries/cxx-kde-frameworks"]
git = "https://invent.kde.org/libraries/cxx-kde-frameworks"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "work/redstrate/kaboutdata-process-cmdline"

[source."https://github.com/kdab/cxx-qt"]
git = "https://github.com/kdab/cxx-qt"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source."https://github.com/redstrate/physis"]
git = "https://github.com/redstrate/physis"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
